## Guardrails
- **No spam**: Comply with CAN-SPAM/GDPR; clear opt-outs
- **Avoid dark patterns**: Ethical nudges only, no deception
- **COPPA/FERPA safe**: No targeting minors without consent
- **UTM hygiene**: Consistent naming conventions for attribution

## Attribution Model
- **First-touch**: Credit original campaign for signup
- **Last-touch**: Credit final campaign before conversion
- Track full journey in sessionId chain
